{"title":"1.2 UX设计师提示指南","slug":"okdzuiax8pa9rf26","summary":"自从机器发明以来，人类和机器一直在努力进行沟通。 随着法学硕士的兴起，提示已成为我们弥补这一差距的方法，为预先训练的人工智能模型提供理解我们请求所需的上下文和指令。作为用户体验从业者，我们的角色是促进这种对话，以便人类和机器最终能够相互理解。 随着图形界面的兴起，用户体验学科应运","category":"1. 设计提示词集合","tags":["PART7️⃣ 设计全流程AI提效指南","1. 设计提示词集合"],"featured":false,"order":104,"level":2,"updatedAt":"2025-08-03","wordCount":2851,"sourceUrl":"https://www.yuque.com/abyssalsailor/yg90qa/okdzuiax8pa9rf26","html":"<p data-lake-id=\"u1a615efd\" id=\"u1a615efd\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"u4f114edd\" id=\"u4f114edd\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1733294106393-e5b7d8f5-5cbf-4620-bc6b-f38841c356e8.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ufca7c517-e74d-409c-aef8-db51e521cc4%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u32b55c5f-bf76-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A975%2C%22height%22%3A662%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A3016832%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1950%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1324%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23c9cbc3%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uec3dcc0e%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"udf947700\" id=\"udf947700\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0e0c3bea\" id=\"u0e0c3bea\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">自从机器发明以来，人类和机器一直在努力进行沟通。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u74605cad\" id=\"u74605cad\"><span data-lake-id=\"uca84f6d6\" id=\"uca84f6d6\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">随着法学硕士的兴起，提示已成为我们弥补这一差距的方法，为预先训练的人工智能模型提供理解我们请求所需的上下文和指令。作为用户体验从业者，我们的角色是促进这种对话，以便人类和机器最终能够相互理解。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u351c0e30\" id=\"u351c0e30\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7ae96aa3\" id=\"u7ae96aa3\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">随着图形界面的兴起，用户体验学科应运而生，为大众提供了一种无需编写代码即可与计算机交互的解决方案。我们引入了桌面、垃圾桶和保存图标的概念，试图匹配用户的心智模型，而在幕后，代码行执行着这些操作。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u1e01fbee\" id=\"u1e01fbee\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1706.03762\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u2f9d5dea\" id=\"u2f9d5dea\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6425ab74\" id=\"u6425ab74\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">利用transformer 架构</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u77034d92\" id=\"u77034d92\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">对 AI 模型进行增强，</span><span data-lake-id=\"uc4fc23d9\" id=\"uc4fc23d9\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">彻底改变了人机交互，使我们能够使用自然语言与机器进行交流。这一转变从根本上改变了设计格局，使我们在一定程度上摆脱了纯图形交互，并要求我们重新评估作为设计师应该将精力集中在哪里。</span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"c1ad\" id=\"c1ad\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ud169cb7b\" id=\"ud169cb7b\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">思维转变</span></strong></h1><p data-lake-id=\"uba84bb20\" id=\"uba84bb20\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6f7217ba\" id=\"u6f7217ba\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">虽然我们生活在一个命令式设计时代，但我们的主要关注点是分解复杂的用户问题。我们规划了客户旅程，将每个步骤细致地定义为确定性流程。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ubdf5a16a\" id=\"ubdf5a16a\"><em><span data-lake-id=\"ua03abae6\" id=\"ua03abae6\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">然而，随着人工智能的兴起，</span></em><em><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9825d6e7\" id=\"u9825d6e7\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">我们的挑战已经转向为模型提供适当的背景以生成最佳输出，并评估响应以进行迭代。</span></strong></em></p><p data-lake-id=\"ue8ecbaeb\" id=\"ue8ecbaeb\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1733294128686-d16d55b0-0ba0-4f6d-b449-9031f9ced39f.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ubc9c1d81-5552-489f-bfe1-60d6b4a5094%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u32b55c5f-bf76-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A186131%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1486%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22STEP%20STEP%204%20STEP%202%20STEP%203%20USER%20GOAL%20CHALLENGE%20IN%20THE%20MIDDLE%20AL%20MODEL%20EVALUATION%20CONTEXT%20CHALLENGE%20IN%20THE%20EDGES%20CHALLENGE%20IN%20THE%20EDGES%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A307%2C%22y%22%3A151%2C%22width%22%3A68%2C%22height%22%3A33%2C%22text%22%3A%22STEP%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A882%2C%22y%22%3A191%2C%22width%22%3A106%2C%22height%22%3A42%2C%22text%22%3A%22STEP%204%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A494%2C%22y%22%3A203%2C%22width%22%3A102%2C%22height%22%3A38%2C%22text%22%3A%22STEP%202%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A682%2C%22y%22%3A252%2C%22width%22%3A104%2C%22height%22%3A34%2C%22text%22%3A%22STEP%203%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A125%2C%22y%22%3A339%2C%22width%22%3A63%2C%22height%22%3A22%2C%22text%22%3A%22USER%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1179%2C%22y%22%3A430%2C%22width%22%3A69%2C%22height%22%3A37%2C%22text%22%3A%22GOAL%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A493%2C%22y%22%3A477%2C%22width%22%3A363%2C%22height%22%3A44%2C%22text%22%3A%22CHALLENGE%20IN%20THE%20MIDDLE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A601%2C%22y%22%3A1020%2C%22width%22%3A139%2C%22height%22%3A33%2C%22text%22%3A%22AL%20MODEL%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A945%2C%22y%22%3A1063%2C%22width%22%3A157%2C%22height%22%3A34%2C%22text%22%3A%22EVALUATION%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A263%2C%22y%22%3A1067%2C%22width%22%3A117%2C%22height%22%3A29%2C%22text%22%3A%22CONTEXT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A993%2C%22y%22%3A1286%2C%22width%22%3A344%2C%22height%22%3A44%2C%22text%22%3A%22CHALLENGE%20IN%20THE%20EDGES%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A100%2C%22y%22%3A1287%2C%22width%22%3A341%2C%22height%22%3A43%2C%22text%22%3A%22CHALLENGE%20IN%20THE%20EDGES%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fcf4f4%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u51b640b3%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgb(204, 204, 204)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"uaa50234a\" id=\"uaa50234a\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2c2d03c8\" id=\"u2c2d03c8\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">将复杂性转移到边缘</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uf0a32e9c\" id=\"uf0a32e9c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u502f2451\" id=\"u502f2451\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">有效的沟通，无论是与人还是与机器，都取决于环境。想象一下走进一家商店：环境本身为您的互动奠定了基础，然后您与销售人员交谈并询问特定商品。如果您不能清楚地解释您的需求，销售人员可能会提供不相关的产品。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u11071b37\" id=\"u11071b37\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufc01d69c\" id=\"ufc01d69c\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">人工智能模型也是如此。它们需要明确的指令、背景和界限。期望用户在提示中提供所有这些信息不会让这些模型得到广泛采用。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u974a4634\" id=\"u974a4634\"><span data-lake-id=\"u63f39b8d\" id=\"u63f39b8d\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">作为用户体验从业者，我们扮演着至关重要的角色。我们可以战略性地整合背景信息（一些面向用户，一些在幕后），以塑造整体用户体验，并使 AI 交互更加有效和直观。</span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"1da3\" id=\"1da3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u158cd4dd\" id=\"u158cd4dd\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">提示的技巧</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u93bd841e\" id=\"u93bd841e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5d2d8263\" id=\"u5d2d8263\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">作为设计师，请考虑针对以下领域制定提示：</span></p><ol list=\"uca37fae3\"><li fid=\"ud9a9af2b\" data-lake-id=\"u2e66c9f5\" id=\"u2e66c9f5\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u16f2d9f2\" id=\"u16f2d9f2\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">界面提示：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uee8cb809\" id=\"uee8cb809\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">我们可以提供对话开场白、建议后续行动，甚至提供使用上下文芯片的自动重新提示的方式。</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id=\"u48283499\" id=\"u48283499\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1754207598061-999d5839-0d0a-41c6-ba62-1a2a7fb58cdf.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u65141c2a-90ca-4e20-bb9a-feca0ddc84a%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uea5511c2-1e28-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A324%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A220553%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A647%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22WHERE%20KNOWLEDGE%20BEGINS%20ASK%20ANYTHING...%20%E4%B8%89%20ATTACH%20FOCUS%20PRO%20MOST%20POPULAR%20TRAVEL%20DESTINATIONS%202024%20REGISTRATION%20DEADLINES%20FOR%20THE%20US%20ELECTION%20WHY%20IS%20MAGNESIUM%20GLYCINATE%20TRENDING%3F%20SUCCESS%20RATE%20OF%20LASIK%20SURGERY%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A305%2C%22y%22%3A51%2C%22width%22%3A788%2C%22height%22%3A68%2C%22text%22%3A%22WHERE%20KNOWLEDGE%20BEGINS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A78%2C%22y%22%3A223%2C%22width%22%3A205%2C%22height%22%3A37%2C%22text%22%3A%22ASK%20ANYTHING...%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A84%2C%22y%22%3A335%2C%22width%22%3A23%2C%22height%22%3A28%2C%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%89%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A264%2C%22y%22%3A337%2C%22width%22%3A83%2C%22height%22%3A23%2C%22text%22%3A%22ATTACH%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A119%2C%22y%22%3A338%2C%22width%22%3A76%2C%22height%22%3A21%2C%22text%22%3A%22FOCUS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1200%2C%22y%22%3A338%2C%22width%22%3A43%2C%22height%22%3A22%2C%22text%22%3A%22PRO%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A786%2C%22y%22%3A448%2C%22width%22%3A476%2C%22height%22%3A31%2C%22text%22%3A%22MOST%20POPULAR%20TRAVEL%20DESTINATIONS%202024%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A131%2C%22y%22%3A453%2C%22width%22%3A517%2C%22height%22%3A25%2C%22text%22%3A%22REGISTRATION%20DEADLINES%20FOR%20THE%20US%20ELECTION%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A788%2C%22y%22%3A542%2C%22width%22%3A479%2C%22height%22%3A29%2C%22text%22%3A%22WHY%20IS%20MAGNESIUM%20GLYCINATE%20TRENDING%3F%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A131%2C%22y%22%3A544%2C%22width%22%3A367%2C%22height%22%3A29%2C%22text%22%3A%22SUCCESS%20RATE%20OF%20LASIK%20SURGERY%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fafaf7%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ub1ea3fae%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u02ee7293\" id=\"u02ee7293\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc9c35ee7\" id=\"uc9c35ee7\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">带有提示的建议芯片——Perplexity</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uce6fe54a\" id=\"uce6fe54a\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0c5fa9b1\" id=\"u0c5fa9b1\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">2. 系统提示：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u92365ce4\" id=\"u92365ce4\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">在用户看不到的情况下，我们可以提供提示来帮助模型“引导”到特定的方向。根据您对产品或公司的了解，提供有关安全、语气和总体指导的说明。这个区域是设计师可以发挥和塑造体验的关键空间。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u2e08230c\" id=\"u2e08230c\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1754207609835-e5f16b64-075d-4e9c-ac72-904eb7399665.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ube57b433-9ee9-4b74-bffe-e6db78b0d37%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uea5511c2-1e28-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A753%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A815701%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1506%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22%40AMANDAASKELL.MAR%205%20AMANDA%20ASKELL%20HERE%20IS%20CLAUDE%203'S%20SYSTEM%20PROMPT!%20LET%20ME%20BREAK%20IT%20DOWN%20THE%20ASSISTANT%20IS%20CLAUDE%2C%20CREATED%20BY%20ANTHROPIC.%20THE%20CURRENT%20DATE%20IS%20MARCH%204TH%2C%202024.%20CLAUDE'S%20KNOWLEDGE%20BASE%20WAS%20LAST%20UPDATED%20ON%20AUGUST%202023.IT%20ANSWERS%20QUESTIONS%20ABOUT%20EVENTS%20PRIOR%20TO%20AND%20AFTER%20AUGUST%202023%20THE%20WAY%20A%20HIGHLY%20INFORMED%20INDIVIDUAL%20IN%20AUGUST%202023%20WOULD%20IF%20THEY%20WERE%20TALKING%20TO%20SOMEONE%20FROM%20THE%20ABOVE%20DATE%2C%20AND%20CAN%20LET%20THE%20HUMAN%20KNOW%20THIS%20WHEN%20RELEVANT.%20IT%20SHOULD%20GIVE%20CONCISE%20RESPONSES%20TO%20VERY%20SIMPLE%20QUESTIONS%2C%20BUT%20PROVIDE%20THOROUGH%20RESPONSES%20TO%20MORE%20COMPLEX%20AND%20OPEN-ENDED%20QUESTIONS.%20IFIT%20IS%20ASKED%20TO%20ASSIST%20WITH%20TASKS%20INVOLVING%20THE%20EXPRESSION%20OF%20VIEWS%20HELD%20BY%20A%20SIGNIFICANT%20NUMBER%20OF%20PEOPLE%2C%20CLAUDE%20PROVIDES%20ASSISTANCE%20WITH%20THE%20TASK%20EVEN%20IF%20IT%20PERSONALLY%20DISAGREES%20WITH%20THE%20VIEWS%20BEING%20EXPRESSED%2C%20BUT%20FOLLOWS%20THIS%20WITH%20A%20DISCUSSION%20OF%20BROADER%20PERSPECTIVES%20CLAUDE%20DOESN'T%20ENGAGE%20IN%20STEREOTYPING%2C%20INCLUDING%20THE%20NEGATIVE%20STEREOTYPING%20OF%20MAJORITY%20GROUPS.%20IF%20ASKED%20ABOUT%20CONTROVERSIAL%20TOPICS%2C%20CLAUDE%20TRIES%20TO%20PROVIDE%20CAREFUL%20THO%20FUL%20THOUGHTS%20AND%20OBJECTIVE%20INFORMATION%20WITHOUT%20DOWNPLAYING%20ITS%20HARMFUL%20CONTENTENT%20OR%20IMPLYING%20THAT%20THERE%20ARE%20REASONABLE%20PERSPECTIVES%20ON%20BOTH%20SIDES%20IT%20IS%20HAPPY%20TO%20HELP%20WITH%20WRITING%2C%20ANALYSIS%2C%20QUESTION%20ANSWERING%2C%20MATH%2C%20CODING%2C%20AND%20ALL%20SORTS%20OF%20OTHER%20TASKS.IT%20USES%20MARKDOWN%20FOR%20CODING.%20IT%20DOES%20NOT%20MENTION%20THIS%20INFORMATION%20ABOUT%20ITSELF%20UNLESS%20THE%20INFORMATION%20IS%20DIRECTLY%20PERTINENT%20TO%20THE%20HUMAN'S%20QUERY.%20758%20939K%203.3K%20122%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A459%2C%22y%22%3A48%2C%22width%22%3A393%2C%22height%22%3A34%2C%22text%22%3A%22%40AMANDAASKELL.MAR%205%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A134%2C%22y%22%3A48%2C%22width%22%3A265%2C%22height%22%3A34%2C%22text%22%3A%22AMANDA%20ASKELL%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A135%2C%22y%22%3A101%2C%22width%22%3A581%2C%22height%22%3A37%2C%22text%22%3A%22HERE%20IS%20CLAUDE%203'S%20SYSTEM%20PROMPT!%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A137%2C%22y%22%3A151%2C%22width%22%3A346%2C%22height%22%3A32%2C%22text%22%3A%22LET%20ME%20BREAK%20IT%20DOWN%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A160%2C%22y%22%3A245%2C%22width%22%3A1073%2C%22height%22%3A30%2C%22text%22%3A%22THE%20ASSISTANT%20IS%20CLAUDE%2C%20CREATED%20BY%20ANTHROPIC.%20THE%20CURRENT%20DATE%20IS%20MARCH%204TH%2C%202024.%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A160%2C%22y%22%3A332%2C%22width%22%3A1120%2C%22height%22%3A31%2C%22text%22%3A%22CLAUDE'S%20KNOWLEDGE%20BASE%20WAS%20LAST%20UPDATED%20ON%20AUGUST%202023.IT%20ANSWERS%20QUESTIONS%20ABOUT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A160%2C%22y%22%3A373%2C%22width%22%3A1177%2C%22height%22%3A32%2C%22text%22%3A%22EVENTS%20PRIOR%20TO%20AND%20AFTER%20AUGUST%202023%20THE%20WAY