%22height%22%3A32%2C%22text%22%3A%22FUL%20THOUGHTS%20AND%20OBJECTIVE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A159%2C%22y%22%3A1011%2C%22width%22%3A1170%2C%22height%22%3A36%2C%22text%22%3A%22INFORMATION%20WITHOUT%20DOWNPLAYING%20ITS%20HARMFUL%20CONTENTENT%20OR%20IMPLYING%20THAT%20THERE%20ARE%20REASONABLE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A158%2C%22y%22%3A1054%2C%22width%22%3A351%2C%22height%22%3A31%2C%22text%22%3A%22PERSPECTIVES%20ON%20BOTH%20SIDES%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A158%2C%22y%22%3A1140%2C%22width%22%3A1187%2C%22height%22%3A29%2C%22text%22%3A%22IT%20IS%20HAPPY%20TO%20HELP%20WITH%20WRITING%2C%20ANALYSIS%2C%20QUESTION%20ANSWERING%2C%20MATH%2C%20CODING%2C%20AND%20ALL%20SORTS%20OF%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A160%2C%22y%22%3A1184%2C%22width%22%3A531%2C%22height%22%3A31%2C%22text%22%3A%22OTHER%20TASKS.IT%20USES%20MARKDOWN%20FOR%20CODING.%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A157%2C%22y%22%3A1265%2C%22width%22%3A1178%2C%22height%22%3A34%2C%22text%22%3A%22IT%20DOES%20NOT%20MENTION%20THIS%20INFORMATION%20ABOUT%20ITSELF%20UNLESS%20THE%20INFORMATION%20IS%20DIRECTLY%20PERTINENT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A160%2C%22y%22%3A1313%2C%22width%22%3A277%2C%22height%22%3A29%2C%22text%22%3A%22TO%20THE%20HUMAN'S%20QUERY.%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A471%2C%22y%22%3A1401%2C%22width%22%3A54%2C%22height%22%3A28%2C%22text%22%3A%22758%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1023%2C%22y%22%3A1402%2C%22width%22%3A86%2C%22height%22%3A27%2C%22text%22%3A%22939K%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A750%2C%22y%22%3A1403%2C%22width%22%3A69%2C%22height%22%3A28%2C%22text%22%3A%223.3K%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A192%2C%22y%22%3A1403%2C%22width%22%3A51%2C%22height%22%3A26%2C%22text%22%3A%22122%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23adadac%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u2521fd6f%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u03f2cb31\" id=\"u03f2cb31\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue11a63db\" id=\"ue11a63db\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">[</span><a href=\"https://x.com/AmandaAskell/status/1765207842993434880/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"ud34af7ee\" id=\"ud34af7ee\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc087a969\" id=\"uc087a969\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">原推文附有 Claude 的系统提示</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u43725d22\" id=\"u43725d22\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">]</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ufd57520c\" id=\"ufd57520c\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf05040e7\" id=\"uf05040e7\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">3. 训练数据促进：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u75964eed\" id=\"u75964eed\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\"> </span><span data-lake-id=\"u8e323bab\" id=\"u8e323bab\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">UX 应该存在，要么帮助训练模型，要么协助对预先训练的模型进行微调。</span></p><ul list=\"u3802bbbd\"><li fid=\"ue888215b\" data-lake-id=\"udefc12d9\" id=\"udefc12d9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u08889d22\" id=\"u08889d22\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">数据集的质量对于模型的最佳性能至关重要，因此了解哪里可能存在潜在的偏见、道德问题甚至冲突的信息至关重要。</span></li><li fid=\"ue888215b\" data-lake-id=\"u136bebf0\" id=\"u136bebf0\"><span data-lake-id=\"uade5fa85\" id=\"uade5fa85\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">我们还可以使用（黄金）提示来帮助创建数据库，以训练特定技能的模型。UX</span><a href=\"https://uxdesign.cc/ai-needs-context-74ed452696e2\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u235b57c7\" id=\"u235b57c7\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub75978e6\" id=\"ub75978e6\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">需要考虑数据集的意图，以及如何创建、整理和与特定用例保持一致</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u3f382f5b\" id=\"u3f382f5b\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u1bf1ecbd\" id=\"u1bf1ecbd\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua11e53e7\" id=\"ua11e53e7\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">如果您的团队没有构建自己的模型或使用开源模型，您可能无法广泛访问数据集。但是，在设计系统提示和用户界面方面仍有大量设计工作要做。与您的团队合作，选择符合用户目标的预训练模型，然后专注于设计使用该模型进行迭代的出色用户体验。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u446d3250\" id=\"u446d3250\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub7519673\" id=\"ub7519673\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">提示工程师需求量很大，他们在训练 AI 模型和开发复杂系统提示方面发挥着至关重要的作用。然而，正如</span><a href=\"https://uxdesign.cc/prompts-should-be-designed-not-engineered-45838a9c3564\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u90beee24\" id=\"u90beee24\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7ade629d\" id=\"u7ade629d\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">Alex Klein</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u2f48f63c\" id=\"u2f48f63c\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">所说，“</span><em><span data-lake-id=\"u035157c5\" id=\"u035157c5\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">提示的复杂性来自于对用户的深刻理解——他们对这种体验的态度和行为——并将这些知识融入到提示中。”</span></em><span data-lake-id=\"u97fa1df9\" id=\"u97fa1df9\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">这种洞察力来自于我们领域内的专业知识，因此我们有责任继续扩展我们的知识。</span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"f926\" id=\"f926\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u80eb7ca0\" id=\"u80eb7ca0\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">了解上下文窗口</span></strong></h1><p data-lake-id=\"ufee1d892\" id=\"ufee1d892\"><span data-lake-id=\"u265ca828\" id=\"u265ca828\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">在这个新的设计领域中，设计师需要掌握的一个关键概念是</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uaead7f28\" id=\"uaead7f28\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">上下文窗口</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7116bcb8\" id=\"u7116bcb8\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">。它指的是模型可以处理以生成输出的信息。在对话界面中，可以将其视为模型可以记住的对话量。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc778c8ea\" id=\"uc778c8ea\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8aea4ab4\" id=\"u8aea4ab4\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">您作为用户输入的每个提示都会影响您在对话中的体验。但是，公司还可以利用上下文窗口（对您隐藏的部分）来添加信息、原则和其他提示。这使他们能够控制输出，确保与公司价值观保持一致，同时仍能满足您的意图。上下文窗口的这个隐藏部分是我们放置系统提示的地方。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u25a1721e\" id=\"u25a1721e\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1733294128503-5e89b2eb-c665-45fe-94cb-788b5fce0625.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ub1144413-7cde-4a61-a8f3-240a47c8165%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u32b55c5f-bf76-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A159220%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1215%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22SYSTEM%20PROMPTS%3A%20COMPANY%20INSTRUCTIONS%2C%20EXAMPLES%20ETC%20CONTEXT%20WINDOW%20TOKENS%20THAT%20THE%20MODEL%20CAN%20EVALUATE%20TO%20GENERATE%20A%20RESPONSE%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A417%2C%22y%22%3A111%2C%22width%22%3A212%2C%22height%22%3A32%2C%22text%22%3A%22SYSTEM%20PROMPTS%3A%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A382%2C%22y%22%3A156%2C%22width%22%3A273%2C%22height%22%3A30%2C%22text%22%3A%22COMPANY%20INSTRUCTIONS%2C%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A437%2C%22y%22%3A195%2C%22width%22%3A168%2C%22height%22%3A30%2C%22text%22%3A%22EXAMPLES%20ETC%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A53%2C%22y%22%3A450%2C%22width%22%3A203%2C%22height%22%3A27%2C%22text%22%3A%22CONTEXT%20WINDOW%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A371%2C%22y%22%3A597%2C%22width%22%3A340%2C%22height%22%3A37%2C%22text%22%3A%22TOKENS%20THAT%20THE%20MODEL%20CAN%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A396%2C%22y%22%3A641%2C%22width%22%3A286%2C%22height%22%3A30%2C%22text%22%3A%22EVALUATE%20TO%20GENERATE%20A%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A482%2C%22y%22%3A685%2C%22width%22%3A115%2C%22height%22%3A29%2C%22text%22%3A%22RESPONSE%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fafafa%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u2e6e72f7%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgb(204, 204, 204)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u632da83b\" id=\"u632da83b\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue4e0bfab\" id=\"ue4e0bfab\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">上下文窗口图</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u4567c211\" id=\"u4567c211\"><span data-lake-id=\"uaa1a8073\" id=\"uaa1a8073\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">上下文窗口以 token 为单位进行衡量，不受时间限制。如果您一个月后返回同一个对话窗口，模型将处理所有之前的互动，只要它们保持在 token 限制之内。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"udcff0f94\" id=\"udcff0f94\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc926e59e\" id=\"uc926e59e\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">行业正在向无限上下文窗口迈进（Gemini 的一个版本目前有 200 万个 token），使模型能够记住您过去的所有对话、想法和您分享的数据。这一转变将带来一系列新挑战，我们作为用户体验设计师需要应对这些挑战。</span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"57a7\" id=\"57a7\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf941aac5\" id=\"uf941aac5\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">如何进行提示</span></strong></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u3b90bf72\" id=\"u3b90bf72\"><span data-lake-id=\"ucdfa45dd\" id=\"ucdfa45dd\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">提示是一个非常反复的过程，你制作一个提示并将其提供给模型，看看你能得到什么回报。然而，</span><span data-lake-id=\"u69758849\" id=\"u69758849\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">你可以使用</span><a href=\"https://www.promptingguide.ai/techniques\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u05fa9a14\" id=\"u05fa9a14\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufbf8dc4a\" id=\"ufbf8dc4a\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">许多技巧来获得更好的结果。</span></a></p><p data-lake-id=\"u602c0e0a\" id=\"u602c0e0a\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub399ba6c\" id=\"ub399ba6c\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">需要记住的是：</span></p><ul list=\"ue322f635\"><li fid=\"u0ce2a575\" data-lake-id=\"u996f126e\" id=\"u996f126e\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4b91ae18\" id=\"u4b91ae18\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">使用框架：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"udcf2eca7\" id=\"udcf2eca7\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">它可以构建信息并帮助在提示中提供上下文。有很多框架，一个很好的例子是</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc3034b41\" id=\"uc3034b41\" style=\"color: currentcolor; background-color: rgb(243, 240, 239)\">种族</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub95a3b02\" id=\"ub95a3b02\" style=\"color: currentcolor; background-color: rgb(243, 240, 239)\">：角色：指定模型所采用的角色/行动：详细说明需要采取的行动/背景：提供情况的相关细节/期望：描述预期结果。</span></li><li fid=\"u0ce2a575\" data-lake-id=\"ue5640dca\" id=\"ue5640dca\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub8215676\" id=\"ub8215676\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">举例说明：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9b6811e8\" id=\"u9b6811e8\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">通过提供示例，您可以为模型提供生成内容和生成方式的背景信息。它演示了生成的响应应该是什么样子。这种技术称为</span><a href=\"https://www.promptingguide.ai/techniques/fewshot\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u5580de66\" id=\"u5580de66\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1044158d\" id=\"u1044158d\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">Few-Shot。</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u6780b6bb\" id=\"u6780b6bb\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">大多数人使用没有示例的提示，只是一个简单的顺序，这被称为零次提示。</span></li><li fid=\"u0ce2a575\" data-lake-id=\"u8f75a5c0\" id=\"u8f75a5c0\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub644a06e\" id=\"ub644a06e\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">要求模型进行推理</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u98442f98\" id=\"u98442f98\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">：放慢回答速度，并要求解释得出答案的步骤将有助于获得更好的输出。我们将其称为</span><a href=\"https://www.promptingguide.ai/techniques/cot\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u0e2a5577\" id=\"u0e2a5577\"><span data-lake-id=\"u373c0c76\" id=\"u373c0c76\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">思维链</span></a><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uceb7d74d\" id=\"uceb7d74d\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">。</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0c9d42f6\" id=\"u0c9d42f6\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">将其与少量提示相结合，可以在需要先推理后回答的更复杂任务上产生更好的结果。最近，OpenAI 宣布了一种新的语言模型 o1，使用强化学习进行复杂推理。它在回答之前会“思考”，从而产生内部思维链以产生更好的反应。</span></li><li fid=\"u0ce2a575\" data-lake-id=\"u7fabcfa2\" id=\"u7fabcfa2\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ucec2bfe9\" id=\"ucec2bfe9\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">明确什么不该做：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u392ff36e\" id=\"u392ff36e\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">通过提供明确的指导方针，说明应该避免什么，包括错误反应的明确例子，模型可以生成更符合您意图的输出。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u621f5c6f\" id=\"u621f5c6f\"><span data-lake-id=\"u937c77dc\" id=\"u937c77dc\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">您可以随时使用这些技巧中的任何一种或全部。</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8d4750d3\" id=\"u8d4750d3\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">通常，如果您以用户的身份接触 AI 模型，您将提供直接而简洁的提示。但是，如果您正在处理系统提示，则这些提示应该更为广泛，例如说明或指南。</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u13370f65\" id=\"u13370f65\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">请参阅以下 AI 意识导师的示例：</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u6f2dfcc9\" id=\"u6f2dfcc9\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1754207618880-643bec67-a265-44ec-887c-4e550d74f58d.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u9b2ee4b0-a0ae-4769-8925-d408af30b43%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uea5511c2-1e28-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A202%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A223387%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A404%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22CONTENT%20YOU%20ARE%20AN%20ALASSISTANT%20WITH%20EXPERTISE%20IN%20MINDFULNESS%20AND%20STRESS%20MANAGEMAGENT.%20YOUR%20TASK%20IS%20TO%20GUIDE%20SYSTEM%20USERS%20THROUGH%20VARIOUS%20NINDFULNESS%20EXERCISES%20AND%20TECHNIQUES%20TO%20HELP%20THELP%20THEN%20REDUCE%20STRESS%2C%20INCREAS%20SELF-AWARENESS%2CAND%20CULTIVATE%20A%20SENSE%20OFINNER%20PEACE.OFFER%20CLEAR%20INSTRUCTIONS%2C%20EXPLANATIONS%2C%20AND%20ENCOURAGEMENT%20TO%20SUPPORT%20THE%20USER'S%20PRACTICE.%20I'VE%20BEEN%20FEELING%20REALLY%20STRESSED%20LATELY%20AND%20WOULD%20LIKE%20TO%20TRY%20SOME%20NINDFULNESS%20EXERCISES%20TO%20HELP%20ME%20USER%20RELAX.CAN%20YOU%20GUIDE%20ME%20THROUGH%20A%20SIMPLE%20MEDITATION%20PRACTICE%3F%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A705%2C%22y%22%3A27%2C%22width%22%3A101%2C%22height%22%3A22%2C%22text%22%3A%22CONTENT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A149%2C%22y%22%3A88%2C%22width%22%3A1191%2C%22height%22%3A27%2C%22text%22%3A%22YOU%20ARE%20AN%20ALASSISTANT%20WITH%20EXPERTISE%20IN%20MINDFULNESS%20AND%20STRESS%20MANAGEMAGENT.%20YOUR%20TASK%20IS%20TO%20GUIDE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A29%2C%22y%22%3A93%2C%22width%22%3A89%2C%22height%22%3A23%2C%22text%22%3A%22SYSTEM%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A146%2C%22y%22%3A128%2C%22width%22%3A1162%2C%22height%22%3A24%2C%22text%22%3A%22USERS%20THROUGH%20VARIOUS%20NINDFULNESS%20EXERCISES%20AND%20TECHNIQUES%20TO%20HELP%20THELP%20THEN%20REDUCE%20STRESS%2C%20INCREAS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A145%2C%22y%22%3A163%2C%22width%22%3A1144%2C%22height%22%3A29%2C%22text%22%3A%22SELF-AWARENESS%2CAND%20CULTIVATE%20A%20SENSE%20OFINNER%20PEACE.OFFER%20CLEAR%20INSTRUCTIONS%2C%20EXPLANATIONS%2C%20AND%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A146%2C%22y%22%3A200%2C%22width%22%3A558%2C%22height%22%3A27%2C%22text%22%3A%22ENCOURAGEMENT%20TO%20SUPPORT%20THE%20USER'S%20PRACTICE.%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A145%2C%22y%22%3A269%2C%22width%22%3A1187%2C%22height%22%3A29%2C%22text%22%3A%22I'VE%20BEEN%20FEELING%20REALLY%20STRESSED%20LATELY%20AND%20WOULD%20LIKE%20TO%20TRY%20SOME%20NINDFULNESS%20EXERCISES%20TO%20HELP%20ME%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A31%2C%22y%22%3A272%2C%22width%22%3A56%2C%22height%22%3A21%2C%22text%22%3A%22USER%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A148%2C%22y%22%3A307%2C%22width%22%3A758%2C%22height%22%3A23%2C%22text%22%3A%22RELAX.CAN%20YOU%20GUIDE%20ME%20THROUGH%20A%20SIMPLE%20MEDITATION%20PRACTICE%3F%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f1f1ee%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u70acde77%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u5da0cb9d\" id=\"u5da0cb9d\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"u18e6a6e8\" id=\"u18e6a6e8\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">[</span><a href=\"https://docs.anthropic.com/en/prompt-library/mindfulness-mentor\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u2e210059\" id=\"u2e210059\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3e2777ce\" id=\"u3e2777ce\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">来自 Anthropic 的示例</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u59857814\" id=\"u59857814\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">]</span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"5a9f\" id=\"5a9f\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue6755c26\" id=\"ue6755c26\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">井然有序</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"ua58f4157\" id=\"ua58f4157\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0defd0a8\" id=\"u0defd0a8\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">提示很快就会变得一团糟，团队成员会添加相互矛盾的信息或低质量的指示。为了最大限度地提高提示的有效性，团队应该采用统一的方法进行协作。这包括决定是通过提示来专注于完善特定技能，还是将公司价值观嵌入系统提示中。这两种方法都可能是正确的，但背后需要有一个策略。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u155c7da1\" id=\"u155c7da1\"><em><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u07ab6afd\" id=\"u07ab6afd\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">系统提示的记录是关键</span></strong></em><em><span data-lake-id=\"uc8f3a57b\" id=\"uc8f3a57b\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">，特别是对于较大的团队来说，以防止重复的努力和可能导致幻觉的相互矛盾的信息。</span></em></p><p data-lake-id=\"u38b44ae6\" id=\"u38b44ae6\"><span data-lake-id=\"u43c550b8\" id=\"u43c550b8\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">提示实验有时会揭示所选 AI 模型的局限性。由于使用 AI 的工作具有高度迭代性，因此有几种解决方案可供考虑：</span></p><ol list=\"u8202256a\"><li fid=\"ufbe8f7ff\" data-lake-id=\"ubc914b47\" id=\"ubc914b47\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4cc74431\" id=\"u4cc74431\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">系统提示：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u29b24ad7\" id=\"u29b24ad7\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">优化系统提示，以减轻限制。</span></li><li fid=\"ufbe8f7ff\" data-lake-id=\"uff2da9f0\" id=\"uff2da9f0\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2d199a09\" id=\"u2d199a09\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">微调：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ued81756b\" id=\"ued81756b\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">与工程师合作定制模型。</span></li><li fid=\"ufbe8f7ff\" data-lake-id=\"u20e4a935\" id=\"u20e4a935\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue16db130\" id=\"ue16db130\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">免责声明：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubc30d548\" id=\"ubc30d548\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">提前告知用户可能存在的限制。</span></li><li fid=\"ufbe8f7ff\" data-lake-id=\"ucd6fc385\" id=\"ucd6fc385\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4eb1e3d7\" id=\"u4eb1e3d7\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">模型更换：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubdeaa72a\" id=\"ubdeaa72a\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">必要时选择更合适的模型。</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id=\"uf4ac28da\" id=\"uf4ac28da\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1a59b473\" id=\"u1a59b473\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">掌握提示的最佳方式就是实践。开始使用您最喜欢的 AI 助手，创建个性化 GPT，或探索 Gemini 的 GEMS。您可以使用提示库，探索不同的技巧，并与可能与您有不同背景的其他人分享。</span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"2a69\" id=\"2a69\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8fc874ec\" id=\"u8fc874ec\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">展望</span></strong></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u385a2e54\" id=\"u385a2e54\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8a5faea5\" id=\"u8a5faea5\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">我们的行业正在快速发展，用户体验正在经历重大变革。许多公司，尤其是小公司，尚未利用用户体验专业知识来推动他们的模型。在其他情况下，公司没有分配足够的资源，因为他们低估了用户体验在这个新领域的复杂性和重要性。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u5e4e1b5c\" id=\"u5e4e1b5c\"><em><span data-lake-id=\"ud154b271\" id=\"ud154b271\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">“我们塑造我们的工具，然后我们的工具塑造我们”——</span></em><em><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u67dc7ff6\" id=\"u67dc7ff6\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">约翰·卡尔金</span></strong></em></p><p data-lake-id=\"ude281f7e\" id=\"ude281f7e\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubbeba4b8\" id=\"ubbeba4b8\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">将用户体验融入塑造模型的责任远大于公司员工人数。这是人机交互发展的决定性时刻，它将塑造下一代。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u76b6ef16\" id=\"u76b6ef16\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5924c50e\" id=\"u5924c50e\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">开始提示，保持愚蠢。</span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"21f8\" id=\"21f8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8b8f6d89\" id=\"u8b8f6d89\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">参考</span></h1><ul list=\"u8f7dd42c\"><li fid=\"ub4e5aed2\" data-lake-id=\"ucee2c76c\" id=\"ucee2c76c\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u18f286dc\" id=\"u18f286dc\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">人机交互指南</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6678f809\" id=\"u6678f809\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">——作者：Eric Horvitz，</span><a href=\"https://erichorvitz.com/Guidelines_Human_AI_Interaction.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u86c7ca20\" id=\"u86c7ca20\"><span data-lake-id=\"uded0c53c\" id=\"uded0c53c\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">https://erichorvitz.com/Guidelines_Human_AI_Interaction.pdf</span></a></li><li fid=\"ub4e5aed2\" data-lake-id=\"ucff006f1\" id=\"ucff006f1\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uad56fcbb\" id=\"uad56fcbb\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">通过系统提示赋予 Claude 一个角色</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8f87ffdc\" id=\"u8f87ffdc\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">— Anthropic 用户指南</span><a href=\"https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/build-with-claude/prompt-engineering/system-prompts\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u6ffded84\" id=\"u6ffded84\"><span data-lake-id=\"u988fed58\" id=\"u988fed58\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/build-with-claude/prompt-engineering/system-prompts</span></a></li><li fid=\"ub4e5aed2\" data-lake-id=\"u69e2335a\" id=\"u69e2335a\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u075f02c6\" id=\"u075f02c6\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">提示应该是设计的，而不是工程化的</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc3424e4e\" id=\"uc3424e4e\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">— Alex Klein</span><span data-lake-id=\"u4ce438c6\" id=\"u4ce438c6\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\"> </span><a href=\"https://uxdesign.cc/prompts-should-be-designed-not-engineered-45838a9c3564\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"uc0d14ca6\" id=\"uc0d14ca6\"><span data-lake-id=\"uabfc139f\" id=\"uabfc139f\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">https://uxdesign.cc/prompts-should-be-designed-not-engineered-45838a9c3564</span></a></li><li fid=\"ub4e5aed2\" data-lake-id=\"u2619efb5\" id=\"u2619efb5\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u62609fa9\" id=\"u62609fa9\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">通过 LLM 学习推理</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5b7154b8\" id=\"u5b7154b8\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">— OpenAI </span><a href=\"https://openai.com/index/learning-to-reason-with-llms/\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u33c026c3\" id=\"u33c026c3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u67f5a6b0\" id=\"u67f5a6b0\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">https://openai.com/index/learning-to-reason-with-llms/</span></a></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u79fa2ddf\" id=\"u79fa2ddf\"><span data-lake-id=\"u024831bb\" id=\"u024831bb\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">​</span><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"u78c1e542\" id=\"u78c1e542\"><span data-lake-id=\"u31ed323a\" id=\"u31ed323a\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">原文链接：</span><a href=\"https://uxdesign.cc/a-ux-designer-guide-to-prompt-f045cd839489?gi=c98ae8c33ea7\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"uf2ea19ac\" id=\"uf2ea19ac\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub323e426\" id=\"ub323e426\">https://uxdesign.cc/a-ux-designer-guide-to-prompt-f045cd839489?gi=c98ae8c33ea7</span></a></p>"}
